HEADWORD: Saucebox
<hw>Sauce"box`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Sauce</er>, and <er>Saucy</er>.]</ety> <def>A saucy, impudent
person; especially, a pert child.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Saucebox, go, meddle with your lady's fan,⟦br⟧
And prate not here!</q> <rj><qau>A. Brewer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Saucepan</ent>⟦br⟧
